  <title translate="true">RMA: Generating the Grid</title>
  <body>
    <header>
      <para styleclass="" style="text-align:left; text-indent:0px; margin-top:0px; margin-right:0px; margin-bottom:10px; margin-left:0px; line-height:2.00; background-color:transparent; white-space:normal; page-break-inside:auto; page-break-after:auto; border:none; tabstops:none;"><text styleclass="Heading1" translate="true">RMA: Generating the Grid</text></para>
    </header>
    <para styleclass="Figure Referrer"><text styleclass="Figure Referrer" translate="true">It is now possible to generate the grid. Generate it by clicking the </text><text styleclass="Figure Referrer" style="font-weight:bold;" translate="true">Generate</text><text styleclass="Figure Referrer" translate="true"> grid button </text><image src="GenerateGrid.png" scale="-99.90%" styleclass="Figure Referrer" figurelistinclude="0"><title translate="true">Generate Grid button</title></image><text styleclass="Figure Referrer" translate="true">. Uncheck the </text><text styleclass="Figure Referrer" style="font-weight:bold;" translate="true">Calculate grid angle automatically</text><text styleclass="Figure Referrer" translate="true"> check box and click the </text><text styleclass="Figure Referrer" style="font-weight:bold;" translate="true">OK</text><text styleclass="Figure Referrer" translate="true"> button. The grid should appear similar to figure 102. The green grid lines indicate that the first row is selected. The blue grid lines indicate that the first column is selected.</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Image"><image src="RmaGridGeneration.bmp" scale="-99.90%" styleclass="Image" figurelistinclude="0"><title translate="true">See caption</title></image></para>
    <para styleclass="Image Caption"><text styleclass="Image Number" translate="true">Figure 102</text><text styleclass="Image Caption" translate="true">. Grid generated for the Rocky Mountain Arsenal.</text></para>
  </body>
